  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个教育系统的数据流图，核心是GradeSync这个成绩同步模块。它要能从ContentCDN获取付费内容，然后有一个判断节点来决定后续走向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，GradeSync作为起始节点，通过\"Get money\"这条线连到ContentCDN。那这个判断节点C也是GradeSync吗？还是一个新的决策点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "判断节点C其实就是GradeSync内部的决策逻辑，所以我希望它显示为{Education_GradeSync}这种菱形。从ContentCDN返回后会进入这个判断。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我现在画好了：GradeSync矩形起步，带\"Get money\"标签的箭头指向ContentCDN，然后从ContentCDN返回进入菱形的GradeSync判断节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "判断节点需要分出三条分支，分别标记为One、Two、Three。其中One走回ContentCDN做内容更新，Two和Three都连到LMS Portal，但是代表不同的业务场景。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Two和Three都指向同一个LMS Portal节点吗？还是拆成两个独立的LMS Portal节点？业务上虽然都是门户，但可能需要区分实例。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "E",
        "F"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "拆成两个独立的节点，都叫Education_LMS_Portal，但一个是Two路径，一个是Three路径。这样视觉上能清楚看出三条分支的完整走向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "E",
        "F"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。现在图里有：GradeSync起始，到ContentCDN获取内容，返回后进入判断菱形，分出三条带标签的线——One回ContentCDN，Two和Three分别指向两个LMS Portal节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C",
        "D",
        "E",
        "F"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才看错了，判断节点C的输入线不应该有标签。从B到C的那条线是直接的返回流，不需要任何标签，只有输出的三条分支需要One、Two、Three。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B",
        "C"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正，B到C的连线现在没有标签了。确认一下现在的结构：A带\"Get money\"到B，B直接到C，C带\"One\"到D，带\"Two\"到E，带\"Three\"到F。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C",
        "D",
        "E",
        "F"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "对的，但D也是ContentCDN对吧？所以One路径是从判断节点返回去更新内容。Two和Three都是进到LMS Portal，只是触发不同的业务流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完全理解。最终图结构：GradeSync启动，付费获取CDN内容，返回后判断——One回CDN更新，Two和Three分别进入两个LMS Portal实例。这样业务闭环就清晰了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
